Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,距离作战结束还有30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你们了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想把我们的古来馆怎样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶  到底在哪儿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哼  你们在往哪儿看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,压杀！章鱼压缩器！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来W算是解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,切  只能持续这么点时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？结束了？哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,来了啊  寺冈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我是不会放弃的  决不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,明香！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也就这点能耐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,明香  你看到我的活跃表现了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  明香  听得见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,明香？明香？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,明香！明香！明香！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到她居然是个机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怪不得有超人一般的黑客能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,具理子  你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那台机器人被我毁掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已经无法阻止小行星的撞击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老老实实成为W吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,具理子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.11,ENCN,,0,0,0,,上校……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.16,ENCN,,0,0,0,,全军覆没……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.11,ENEN,,0,0,0,,Colonel ……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.16,ENEN,,0,0,0,,our troops have been wiped out ……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,具理子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,派因！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  明香…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还像以前一样给我下指示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,成木野  你是为了成为英雄而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,无法逃避的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的  小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我是英雄  所以决不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个都住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,千代子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,派因！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  千代子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想被你们打乱计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,明香…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,具理子  你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你和千代子怎么可能会明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经所体验到的绝望…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃了一切  除了接受别无选择
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能明白我的孤独！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不让这样的不幸重演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我必须要将他们全部杀掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈  终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快把那只小熊交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,千代子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样！住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你是从哪儿知道我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我就送你上黄泉路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,该上路的是你才对！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是神圣的神仙之酒  神酒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.74,TIPSS2,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H3A77EE&\fad(500,500)\3c&H000200&}辅助动力启动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小爱…我有事拜托你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？明香？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间了…听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一发…还有一发…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托把我扶到那里坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,具理子你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,临兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,临兵斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,临兵斗者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,临兵斗者皆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,临兵斗者皆阵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,临兵斗者皆阵列
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,临兵斗者皆阵列在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,临兵斗者皆阵列在前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,具理子你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,具理子你这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,恶灵退散！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,通告「Justic  Punch」全体成员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,作战圆满成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,重复
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,通告「Justic  Punch」全体成员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,作战圆满成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,千代子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,傻瓜  你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,千代子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,帕因  等到了夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起去捉夹子虫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好大好大的扁夹子虫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在草原上捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,用纸箱做的滑橇滑下山坡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,用白三叶草编成花冠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,去田地里摘西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,三个人一起再次快乐地玩耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  千代子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  请醒一醒！睁开眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我希望的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,即使拯救了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没有你的未来  又有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来还没死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是那么单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要三个人一起超人化才能做到不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,从那个水坝上掉下时的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你们刚才为什么吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为具理子给了帕因奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是结婚戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,结…结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我只说是誓约之戒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？有三个？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我做了三个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,千代子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,帕因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那就让我们起誓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们三人  无论遇到什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,永远都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:13:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  我们赶在太阳落山前回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,回到和那时相同的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  具理子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,活着来赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  住手  帕因！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,帕因！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:15:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,千代子  我把这个身体还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,约定…不是已经说好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里…不要这样  帕因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你  不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:30.50,TIPSS4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\c&H040404&\3c&HFEFEFE&\pos(640,434)}49天后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,General  Liberal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Deflation  Spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Natural  mineral
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现身吧  游太的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,首先我要说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,成木野  你就不能换身衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可是  我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在拉芙拉身体里的是一直灵魂出窍的那个游太吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  是去年12月21日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在河边被未来的自己夺去身体的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  你真的要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉要冷清下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我有必须要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,回到25年前  附身到5岁的拉芙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把明香的设计图和未来的指示发传真给灵像交是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,之后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,穿越到去年的12月21日  重复同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,进入在河边晕倒的我自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不用想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要创造自己美好的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,而我  这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,创造一个非常幸福和谐的未来是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  这是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天已经是另一个游太走了之后的第49天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好地供奉他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大家的供品都带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,安心成佛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是小爱的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,波斯猫的一种  金吉拉猫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一个专科的朋友求我收养的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要不  要不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要不就叫千良之助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.98,TIPSS2,,0,0,0,,{\an7}吉拉和千良同音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很好听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哼唧  你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,站住  千良之助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,诶  等一下  你怎么了  振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:59.89,TIPSS4,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs100\fn蒙纳简超刚黑\pos(640,639)}向着最幸福和平的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:28.85,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}バラバラになった心の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:33.73,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}この世界と繋ぐ光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:38.09,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}確かな思いを  My friend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:42.83,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}また会えるって誓ったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:48.57,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}約束のあの場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:01.76,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}今日は歩こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:06.40,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}息切らし笑った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:11.03,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}バス亭と並んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:15.81,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}不揃いな影法師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:24.49,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}運命は悪戯な笑顔で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:29.39,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}ただ頼りなく結んだ糸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:36.10,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}あの日引きちぎっただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:40.55,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}同じ夢を見た  My dear friends
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:49.73,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}遠く遠く離れててもいつか巡り会えるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:54.32,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}約束の彼方で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:59.19,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}目眩く日々の途中で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:03.85,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}忘れない　忘れたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:14.21,MJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}同じ空の下でみんな今日も歩いてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:28.85,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}四分五裂的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:33.73,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}连接这世界的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:38.09,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}最真切的思念  My friend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:42.83,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我们曾为再会而立下誓言了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:48.57,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}在那约定的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:01.76,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}今天就迈开脚步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:06.40,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}喘息的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:11.03,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}就在巴士车站旁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:15.81,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}散乱的人影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:24.49,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}命运以恶作剧般的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:29.39,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}胡闹似地结下绳索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:36.10,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}却又在那一天扯断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:40.55,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}梦见相同的梦  My dear friends
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:49.73,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}哪怕相隔万里  我们也仍能再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:54.32,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}就在那个约定的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:59.19,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}即使在眩目的漫长旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:03.85,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}无法忘记  不想忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:14.21,MCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}今天大家也都走在这同一片天空下
